00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,390
Your Majesty, this...

291
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,310
Your Majesty,

292
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:45,510
how can you pry into

293
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:47,840
an official's private affairs like this?

294
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,500
Then let me ask it another way.

295
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:52,360
Chen Yanyun.

296
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,750
I heard

297
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:56,030
that Miss Gu's maternal family

298
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,430
are your surbordinates.

299
00:14:57,600 --> 00:15:00,000
Have you two been
in contact for a long time?

300
00:15:02,150 --> 00:15:02,950
Your Majesty.

301
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:05,750
I still have many memorials to review.

302
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:08,390
You and Jiuheng
can take your time talking.

303
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,190
I shall take my leave now.

304
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:13,210
Zhang Fang,

305
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,790
see Mr. Fu out for me.

306
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,360
Yes, Your Majesty.

307
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:19,510
Take care, Mentor.

308
00:15:26,670 --> 00:15:27,470
Your Majesty.

309
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:29,550
Miss Gu and I...

310
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:31,720
I am hungry.

311
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:33,800
Go get me some snacks.

312
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,320
Yes, Your Majesty.

313
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,360
Today,

314
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,270
an imperial censor impeached

315
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:55,870
the Marquis Changxing
for great disrespect.

316
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:57,930
Mr. Fu wants to deal with it severely.

317
00:15:58,080 --> 00:16:00,960
But I want to protect
Marquis Changxing's household.

318
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,750
However,

319
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:03,550
I cannot openly go against Mr. Fu.

320
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:04,360
So I can only

321
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,550
entrust this to you.

322
00:16:21,270 --> 00:16:21,840
But what I

323
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:23,390
never expected was that

324
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,720
His Majesty would so directly ask you

325
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:27,630
to protect
the Marquis Changxing's household.

326
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:28,750
Isn't this clearly

327
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:32,000
forcing you to oppose
the Senior Grand Secretary?

328
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:34,800
Could he be testing you on purpose?

329
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,150
It is a test,

330
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:41,790
but also an order.

331
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:43,870
The disaster relief grain case

332
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:45,150
fell entirely on the Ministry of Revenue,

333
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,610
and I shouldered it alone.

334
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:48,030
Although this idea

335
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:49,690
was proposed by Wang Xuanfan,

336
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:52,080
Mentor remained completely silent

337
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,340
from beginning to end.

338
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,560
This is enough for His Majesty to infer

339
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:58,510
that it was tacitly approved by Mentor.

340
00:16:58,510 --> 00:16:59,440
At the same time,

341
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,630
His Majesty may also suspect that

342
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:02,670
Mentor and I

343
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,069
could develop a rift

344
00:17:04,069 --> 00:17:05,069
over this matter.

345
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:10,510
His Majesty

346
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:13,780
has grown faster

347
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:14,880
than we expected.

348
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:21,200
But even with an imperial edict,

349
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,440
if the Senior Grand Secretary
is determined

350
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,349
bring down
the Marquis Changxing's household,

351
00:17:25,349 --> 00:17:26,720
what can you do?

352
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,510
Let's go see Ye Xian first.

353
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:46,750
Third Master.

354
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:47,960
-Third Master!
-Don't move.

355
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,030
Chen Yanyun.

356
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:52,860
Ye Xian,

357
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,110
are you crazy?

358
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,900
I've always been a madman.

359
00:17:55,900 --> 00:17:56,880
Go to hell!

360
00:18:00,030 --> 00:18:00,550
My Lord!

361
00:18:01,570 --> 00:18:02,460
[Prosperity of Parents]

362
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:02,600
Stay back!

363
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:11,770
The imperial censor impeached
your father for grave disrespect.

364
00:18:11,770 --> 00:18:14,030
His Majesty has ordered severe punishment.

365
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:14,870
Yet you still have the leisure

366
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:16,470
for matters of romance here.

367
00:18:21,620 --> 00:18:27,790
[Prosperity of Parents]

368
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,510
My Lord.

369
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:26,020
Miss Gu and I are in love.

370
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:28,200
How could you possibly separate us?

371
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:30,060
It's simply wishful thinking.

372
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,030
Chen Yanyun.

373
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:34,430
I am sworn to
be your irreconcilable enemy.

374
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:37,550
[Prosperity of Parents]

375
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:41,760
Third Master.

376
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,790
Spread word of what happened today—

377
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:44,920
Xian Ye's public assassination attempt,

378
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:46,200
the carriage stop, and his jealousy

379
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:46,790
over me.

380
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:49,960
Make it as widely known as possible.

381
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:51,270
Okay.

382
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:55,720
The Marquis Changxing, Ye Guangsheng,

383
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,970
disobeyed the late Emperor
and showed disrespect to His Majesty,

384
00:18:57,970 --> 00:18:59,010
acted obstinately and arrogantly,

385
00:18:59,010 --> 00:19:00,110
and failed in his duties.

386
00:19:00,110 --> 00:19:01,440
The Penal Court is hereby ordered

387
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:03,510
to immediately arrest the
Marquis Changxing,

388
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:04,720
and investigate the matter thoroughly

389
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,520
to appease His Majesty's wrath.

390
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:16,200
I, Ye Xian,

391
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:18,640
receive the decree.

392
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,030
My Lord.

393
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:30,240
Let's go.

394
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:33,210
Come with me to the Marquis' residence

395
00:19:34,610 --> 00:19:36,470
to arrest the Marquis Changxing.

396
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:39,830
This...

397
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:52,920
[Marquis Changxing's Mansion]

398
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,790
Come in after an hour.

399
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:04,680
Yes, my lord!

400
00:20:07,650 --> 00:20:09,720
[Marquis Changxing's Mansion]

401
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:21,220
[Marquis Changxing's Mansion]

402
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:24,590
My Lord, Madam.

403
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:25,790
Young Lord Ye is back.

404
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:34,640
Father. Mother.

405
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:38,060
So you do know how to come back.

406
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:40,680
Xian.

407
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:45,370
You've lost weight.

408
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,740
And you're darker too.

409
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:50,550
You haven't eaten yet, right?

410
00:20:50,550 --> 00:20:52,610
Why don't you sit down and eat with us?

411
00:20:59,350 --> 00:21:00,590
If you don't want to eat, that's fine too.

412
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:01,450
Let's eat then.

413
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:04,200
Okay.

414
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,240
Come.

415
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,000
Hurry.

416
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:10,200
Tell the kitchen

417
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:12,160
to add a plate
of stir-fried pork with yellow chives,

418
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,340
radish meatball soup,

419
00:21:13,340 --> 00:21:14,310
and those

420
00:21:14,310 --> 00:21:15,510
meat-filled flatbreads.

421
00:21:15,510 --> 00:21:16,350
Xian

422
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,310
loves those the most.

423
00:21:17,310 --> 00:21:18,270
Yes, Madam.

424
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:22,160
Xian,

425
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:24,550
is your work at the Penal Court

426
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,870
very busy?

427
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,070
It's fine.

428
00:21:27,830 --> 00:21:29,160
What do you mean "fine"?

429
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:32,310
I heard you went to Shanxi earlier

430
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,880
and almost lost your life.

431
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,830
Is that true?

432
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,760
How could it be so dangerous?

433
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,220
Isn't Father also in constant danger

434
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:42,720
of losing his life on the battlefield?

435
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:44,770
What I do is different.

436
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:46,580
I was fighting enemies.

437
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,300
But what about you?

438
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:50,790
You've become a tool
in their factional struggles,

439
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:51,440
a blade

440
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,440
in His Majesty's hand.

441
00:21:56,310 --> 00:21:58,040
It's rare for him to come back.

442
00:21:58,110 --> 00:21:59,240
Why are you saying all this?

443
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,070
Am I wrong?

444
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:02,810
Go out and ask around what kind of work

445
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:04,090
the Penal Court

446
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:05,720
does every day.

447
00:22:06,310 --> 00:22:07,590
In this vast court,

448
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:10,040
who is not the His Majesty's blade?

449
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:12,200
And who would dare not be his blade?

450
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:12,640
You...

451
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,490
You are an educated person.

452
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:17,510
Have you learned all that scholarship

453
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:19,400
just to feed it to the dogs?

454
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,640
I don't care what you think.

455
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:24,030
Tomorrow I will submit a memorial
to the Empress Dowager

456
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:26,360
and have you removed from the Penal Court.

457
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:26,920
I've already

458
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,380
talked to your Uncle Song.

459
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,590
You will be transferred
to the Ministry of War.

460
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:31,200
I won't go.

461
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:32,440
Uncle Song

462
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:33,970
won't listen to you either.

463
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:36,580
You brat, how dare you defy me!

464
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:47,940
Marquis Changxing, receive the decree.

465
00:23:01,010 --> 00:23:07,150
[Great Merit and High Esteem]

466
00:23:12,590 --> 00:23:13,270
My Lord.

467
00:23:17,830 --> 00:23:18,960
I do not accept this.

468
00:23:20,070 --> 00:23:21,900
Since His Majesty ascended the throne,

469
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:24,900
I have not stepped
out of the residence due to illness.

470
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,760
What crime have I committed?

471
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:30,000
If you have any objections,

472
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:33,240
you can state them in the imperial prison.

473
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:35,160
The imperial command cannot be delayed.

474
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:36,590
I will wait outside.

475
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:38,590
Please come out

476
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,850
within 15 minutes.

477
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:41,830
Xian!

478
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,310
Mother,

479
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,440
I am also...

480
00:23:44,510 --> 00:23:46,680
You unfilial son!

481
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:55,110
Are you trying to kill your own father?

482
00:24:00,150 --> 00:24:09,590
[Great Merit and High Esteem]

483
00:24:08,830 --> 00:24:09,510
My Lord.

484
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:31,880
If I were you,

485
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,760
I would request to be imprisoned as well.

486
00:24:34,760 --> 00:24:35,540
That way,

487
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:37,960
at least in the Penal Court,

488
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:40,110
no one would be able
to move against the Marquis.

489
00:24:40,110 --> 00:24:42,640
And he would secure
a slim chance of survival.

490
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,010
Why should I trust you?

491
00:24:49,810 --> 00:24:50,820
My Lord.

492
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:52,610
Vice Commander Hu.

493
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:59,430
[A Legacy of Virtue and Grace]

494
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:53,680
My Lord.

495
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:58,710
Since the imperial censor impeached
Marquis Changxing for disrespect,

496
00:24:58,710 --> 00:25:00,720
as the heir of the Marquis's household,

497
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:03,120
I should also be imprisoned
to await trial.

498
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,570
Vice Commander Hu, please bind me as well.

499
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,240
You unfilial son!

500
00:25:07,330 --> 00:25:08,390
What are you doing?

501
00:25:08,450 --> 00:25:09,020
My Lord.

502
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,620
Is this really necessary?

503
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:11,640
What?

504
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:13,880
Does no one

505
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,210
obey my orders anymore?

506
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:18,640
Okay.

507
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,200
Xian, you can't go.

508
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,110
Don't go!

509
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:26,920
Xian!

510
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,070
No, Xian.

511
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,850
No!

512
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:36,270
Xian!

513
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,310
No!

514
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:39,000
Madam.

515
00:25:39,830 --> 00:25:42,200
Xian, you can't go!

516
00:25:42,830 --> 00:25:43,590
Your Lordship!

517
00:25:43,590 --> 00:25:44,550
Xian!

518
00:25:45,510 --> 00:25:46,310
Chen Yanyun.

519
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:48,810
I have acted according to the plan.

520
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,600
If you dare to deceive me,

521
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,680
I will tear you to pieces.

522
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:57,830
My Lord.

523
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:06,110
Third Master.

524
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,920
Last night, Young Lord Ye

525
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,960
personally went to the Marquis' residence
to arrest Marquis Changxing

526
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:11,480
and then requested
to be imprisoned as well.

527
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,610
Now they've been taken away together.

528
00:26:15,510 --> 00:26:16,680
I was worried

529
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:18,030
that because of Miss Gu,

530
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:19,760
he wouldn't trust you anymore.

531
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:20,850
I didn't expect him

532
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:22,400
to actually do it.

533
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,530
He's quite a character.

534
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:28,030
So what should

535
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:30,880
we do next?

536
00:26:34,830 --> 00:26:35,760
Build momentum.

537
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,440
Build momentum?

538
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:44,270
Marquis Changxing enjoys immense prestige.

539
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:44,960
Mentor

540
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,960
not only wants Marquis Changxing's life,

541
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:47,830
but also wants to destroy

542
00:26:47,830 --> 00:26:49,000
his reputation.

543
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:53,200
But His Majesty wants to protect
Marquis Changxing's household.

544
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,030
He will find no support

545
00:26:54,030 --> 00:26:55,200
within the court.

546
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:57,840
We can only make efforts
outside the court.

547
00:26:58,400 --> 00:26:59,440
Ye Xian arresting his own father

548
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,590
defies social conventions.

549
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:02,200
And his voluntary imprisonment

550
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,910
only further proves his innocence.

551
00:27:03,910 --> 00:27:05,170
These two points alone

552
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:07,440
will cause a sensation in the capital.

553
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:09,040
If we build enough momentum,

554
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:13,010
His Majesty will
have grounds to intervene.

555
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:14,400
Then we can find a way

556
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:17,000
to get them a lighter sentence.

557
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,270
Brilliant.

558
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:22,510
Among all crimes since ancient times,

559
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:25,790
the crime of great disrespect
is the most elusive.

560
00:27:25,790 --> 00:27:26,990
It is based on hearsay

561
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:28,400
and lacks any evidence.

562
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,590
It is truly the most convenient charge

563
00:27:30,590 --> 00:27:32,110
for framing someone.

564
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:35,370
Precisely because there is no evidence,

565
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,920
it can be dealt with

566
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:39,930
either severely

567
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,680
or lightly.

568
00:27:52,830 --> 00:27:54,510
But all I can do

569
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:58,270
is preserve the Marquis's reputation.

570
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,900
As for saving his life—

571
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:03,750
it will be difficult.

572
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,160
Ruixiang,

573
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,500
get me another pot.

574
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:21,440
Stop drinking.

575
00:28:21,830 --> 00:28:23,430
You've already had two pots.

576
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:24,440
You always

577
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:25,720
look down on people

578
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:27,110
who drown their sorrows in drink,

579
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:28,570
and say they are pathetic.

580
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:29,660
If they truly get angry,

581
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:30,830
just kill someone.

582
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:33,590
So why are you acting like this now?

583
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,720
Kill someone?

584
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:35,750
Kill who?

585
00:28:36,550 --> 00:28:37,350
Your brother?

586
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,510
I can't beat him.

587
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:40,590
And I can't bear to hurt Ye Xian.

588
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,590
Maybe,

589
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:45,000
I should just kill

590
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,310
Gu Jinzhao.

591
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:47,640
Stop talking nonsense.

592
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:49,640
You two don't have that much bad blood.

593
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,510
Don't tell me

594
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:51,920
you like my brother?

595
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,760
Who told you I like your brother?

596
00:28:54,310 --> 00:28:55,640
He's full of schemes.

597
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,320
I like Ye Xian.

598
00:28:58,720 --> 00:28:59,750
There you go.

599
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,680
Jinzhao doesn't like Ye Xian.

600
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,030
No one's trying to take him from you.

601
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:04,350
That's exactly the problem.

602
00:29:04,350 --> 00:29:06,080
I'd rather she fight me for him,

603
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:07,510
so we could

604
00:29:07,510 --> 00:29:08,960
settle it head-on.

605
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,200
But look at things now.

606
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,110
She doesn't care at all,

607
00:29:11,110 --> 00:29:12,680
while Ye Xian has lost his mind—

608
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:13,960
storming into the Gu residence
and even trying

609
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:16,590
to assassinate your brother
in broad daylight.

610
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:18,250
Though, he does have my style.

611
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,720
Yeah.

612
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,440
I didn't expect Ye Xian

613
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:24,310
to like Jinzhao so much.

614
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:26,000
And I really didn't expect

615
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:26,480
Yanyun

616
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,880
to like her that much either.

617
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:28,590
Let me tell you.

618
00:29:28,590 --> 00:29:29,400
Yanyun even stood up

619
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,530
to my mother for her,

620
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:31,640
and specially

621
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:33,510
asked Madam He to act as matchmaker.

622
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:34,640
I've never seen him

623
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:36,510
like someone so much.

624
00:29:37,070 --> 00:29:38,960
But it makes sense.

625
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:39,880
Jinzhao

626
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,280
is really quite lovable.

627
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,510
Who said she's lovable?

628
00:29:43,830 --> 00:29:45,200
She's not honest at all.

629
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:47,160
She clearly knows I like Ye Xian.

630
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,000
So why didn't she tell me

631
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,200
that he likes her?

632
00:29:49,750 --> 00:29:51,000
She just wanted to make a fool of me.

633
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,350
Don't be mad.

634
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,270
I don't think Jinzhao

635
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:55,800
kept it from you on purpose.

636
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:56,790
Think about it.

637
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,350
She is an unmarried girl,

638
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,830
and she is not that close to you.

639
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:01,000
If you suddenly told her

640
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,000
you liked Ye Xian,

641
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,310
what was she supposed to say?

642
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:03,960
Was she supposed to say,

643
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,350
"Don't like him. He likes me,

644
00:30:05,350 --> 00:30:06,550
but I don't like him"?

645
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:07,400
You...

646
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:09,800
Are you trying to confuse me?

647
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,310
Anyway, whether it was intentional

648
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:14,240
or not,

649
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,700
she is my rival in love now.

650
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:17,280
I won't be friends with her.

651
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:20,340
You are not allowed to either.

652
00:30:20,830 --> 00:30:22,630
I won't be on good terms with her.

653
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,640
Anyway, she is my third sister-in-law.

654
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,750
You bad girl.

655
00:30:26,750 --> 00:30:27,590
Come here.

656
00:30:27,830 --> 00:30:28,790
My Lady. My Lady.

657
00:30:28,790 --> 00:30:29,920
Something's wrong.

658
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,510
Young Lord Ye

659
00:30:33,510 --> 00:30:35,200
has been imprisoned in the Penal Court.

660
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:35,790
What?

661
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:37,130
What happened?

662
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:38,720
They said
an imperial censor has impeached

663
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,160
the Marquis Changxing
for great disrespect,

664
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,510
and His Majesty ordered
to punish him severely.

665
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:42,070
Young Lord Ye

666
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:43,550
personally went to arrest the Marquis,

667
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:46,010
and then requested
to be imprisoned as well.

668
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:49,030
Can you go

669
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:50,200
and beg Chen Yanyun for me?

670
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,460
Ask him to save Ye Xian.

671
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:52,680
I...

672
00:30:53,350 --> 00:30:54,680
Yanyun never allows the family

673
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:56,410
to interfere in court affairs.

674
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:59,120
I'm afraid my words
won't carry any weight.

675
00:31:00,830 --> 00:31:01,310
Fine.

676
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:04,020
Your words hold no weight, right?

677
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:04,750
Then I'll go find

678
00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:06,080
someone whose words do.

679
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,070
What?

680
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:16,110
Ye Xian has been imprisoned
in the Penal Court?

681
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,710
It happened just last night.

682
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,310
Rumor has it that

683
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:20,510
the Marquis Changxing

684
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,590
has committed a grave offense.

685
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:22,790
And the court will deal with it severely.

686
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:23,750
They even locked up Young Lord Ye

687
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:24,920
and the Marquis.

688
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,550
Zhao.

689
00:31:29,790 --> 00:31:30,550
Fifth Aunt.

690
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:32,160
Ye Xian and my father

691
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:34,030
have been imprisoned in the Penal Court.

692
00:31:34,030 --> 00:31:34,590
Right now,

693
00:31:34,590 --> 00:31:35,750
I have no other way out.

694
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:36,950
I have to come beg you.

695
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,920
Can you please help me

696
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,250
and plead with Lord Chen

697
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,140
to save Xian and my father?

698
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,240
Please don't do this.

699
00:31:44,240 --> 00:31:44,920
Get up.

700
00:31:45,510 --> 00:31:46,640
I heard about it too,

701
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:48,000
so I was about to go find Third Master

702
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:48,980
to think of a way.

703
00:31:49,550 --> 00:31:50,950
You are not allowed to go.

704
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:57,240
Lady Ye.

705
00:31:58,790 --> 00:32:00,110
Didn't I warn you

706
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:02,140
not to come to Zhao?

707
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:03,770
Why didn't you listen?

708
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:05,440
The other day, Ye Xian

709
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,700
made such a huge scene.

710
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:09,400
How do you still
have the nerve to ask Zhao

711
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,750
to plead with Lord Chen?

712
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,370
Don't you know

713
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,030
what crime Marquis Changxing
has committed?

714
00:32:15,030 --> 00:32:16,200
It's a charge of great disrespect—

715
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:18,130
enough to wipe out the entire clan!

716
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:19,160
Do you think

717
00:32:19,510 --> 00:32:20,720
our Gu family hasn't suffered

718
00:32:20,720 --> 00:32:21,650
enough already?

719
00:32:22,350 --> 00:32:23,550
You're dragging our Gu family into this

720
00:32:23,550 --> 00:32:25,270
just for your own household.

721
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,510
Don't forget

722
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:29,550
you are a daughter-in-law of our family.

723
00:32:29,550 --> 00:32:31,070
I am a daughter-in-law of the Gu family,

724
00:32:31,070 --> 00:32:33,400
but I am even more
a daughter of the Ye family.

725
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:34,680
If you're afraid of
being implicated by me,

726
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,510
then have Dexiu write a letter of divorce.

727
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,510
Do you think we wouldn't dare

728
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:38,480
to write it?

729
00:32:39,350 --> 00:32:40,280
I'm warning you.

730
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,750
The current Marquis household

731
00:32:42,750 --> 00:32:43,880
cannot protect you.

732
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:45,960
Well.

733
00:32:46,830 --> 00:32:48,880
When the Marquis household was in power,

734
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,030
you came crawling to me

735
00:32:50,030 --> 00:32:51,160
time and time again.

736
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:53,380
Now that we're in trouble,

737
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:55,000
you immediately turn your backs on us

738
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,230
and avoid us like the plague.

739
00:32:56,230 --> 00:32:57,960
What a snobbish attitude.

740
00:32:59,310 --> 00:33:01,310
If you want to write
a letter of divorce, go ahead.

741
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:03,970
I'm the one who finds
your Gu family disgusting.

742
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:05,480
Zhao.

743
00:33:06,270 --> 00:33:07,730
I'm not talking about you.

744
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:08,550
I know I may

745
00:33:08,570 --> 00:33:09,770
be asking too much,

746
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,550
but I have no other way right now—

747
00:33:11,550 --> 00:33:13,080
I can only beg for your help.

748
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,830
Fifth Aunt, don't panic.

749
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,600
Since I promised to help you,

750
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:17,680
I definitely will.

751
00:33:17,680 --> 00:33:18,510
Zhao.

752
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:21,040
Grandmother.

753
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,720
Right now, even if you ask Fifth Uncle

754
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,110
to write a divorce letter for Fifth Aunt,

755
00:33:24,110 --> 00:33:25,510
it's too late to cut ties.

756
00:33:26,030 --> 00:33:26,960
If the Marquis household falls,

757
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:27,960
do you think there will be

758
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:29,560
any benefit to our Gu family?

759
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:30,460
We are family.

760
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:31,550
If we don't help now,

761
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:32,510
when will we?

762
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:33,720
Zhao.

763
00:33:33,740 --> 00:33:35,350
I heard rumors that

764
00:33:35,550 --> 00:33:38,750
Ye Xian tried to assassinate
Lord Chen in broad daylight.

765
00:33:39,070 --> 00:33:40,000
I heard that too.

766
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,310
That is why

767
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:42,770
I must go take a look.

768
00:33:50,270 --> 00:33:51,070
Qinglan.

769
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:56,030
You are also here

770
00:33:56,030 --> 00:33:57,550
for Ye Xian?

771
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,270
You're smart.

772
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:01,070
If you still consider Ye Xian

773
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:02,000
a friend,

774
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,550
then go and ask Chen Yanyun

775
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:04,480
to help save him.

776
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,190
Have a seat.

777
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,510
How is it?

778
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,590
Is there still any hope for
the Marquis Changxing's household?

779
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:35,050
There wasn't any at first.

780
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:35,800
But

781
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:38,960
Ye Xian went to prison
along with the Marquis Changxing—

782
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:39,960
so that's created

783
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,679
a slim chance of turning things around.

784
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,710
Right.

785
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,000
On the day of the palace coup,

786
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:50,150
Marquis Changxing was accused of treason.

787
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:52,440
Ye Xian risked his life
to protect His Majesty,

788
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:55,150
which made the charge of treason
fall apart on its own.

789
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:57,150
Now that Ye Xian has been imprisoned

790
00:34:57,190 --> 00:34:58,720
together with the Marquis,

791
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:02,140
it may achieve a similar effect.

792
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,420
It's not just that.

793
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:05,670
Ye Xian going into prison

794
00:35:05,670 --> 00:35:07,600
can also protect the Marquis a bit.

795
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:08,890
What do you mean?

796
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:10,410
Is someone planning to

797
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:12,070
move against the Marquis in prison?

798
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:13,440
It's just a precaution.

799
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:18,880
Do you have any way to save Ye Xian?

800
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,070
I do,

801
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:21,440
but

802
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:25,010
it will require you
to suffer some grievance.

803
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:31,280
For the Ye family case,

804
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,940
you should be the chief judge.

805
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:35,300
But I

806
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:37,060
haven't been reinstated yet.

807
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,880
After you finish

808
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:43,150
judging Marquis Changxing,

809
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:45,950
you can return to
the Hall of Literary Profundity.

810
00:35:46,630 --> 00:35:47,690
Thank you, mentor.

811
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:49,320
However,

812
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:50,920
I think

813
00:35:51,550 --> 00:35:53,480
it's still not quite appropriate.

814
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,130
I've heard about it.

815
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:01,320
Ye Xian

816
00:36:02,150 --> 00:36:04,070
actually attempted to assassinate

817
00:36:04,070 --> 00:36:06,150
a Grand Secretary in broad daylight.

818
00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:07,880
Truly appalling.

819
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:10,590
It is just that you are magnanimous.

820
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,950
Otherwise, this alone

821
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:15,130
would be enough to condemn

822
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,340
Marquis Changxing's household.

823
00:36:20,550 --> 00:36:22,280
My apologies for this, mentor.

824
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:23,920
I originally thought

825
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:25,750
it was just a private matter,

826
00:36:26,030 --> 00:36:28,160
and blowing it up wouldn't do any good.

827
00:36:28,230 --> 00:36:29,150
But now

828
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,800
it's known to
the whole court and the public.

829
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:34,030
Everyone says
the feud between Ye Xian and me

830
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:35,160
is irreconcilable.

831
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,670
If I were now

832
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:38,710
to try the Ye family case,

833
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,560
I fear people would accuse me

834
00:36:41,710 --> 00:36:44,360
of using my public office
to settle personal scores.

835
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,630
Let them talk.

836
00:36:46,260 --> 00:36:47,510
Whoever protests the loudest

837
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:49,770
is part of Marquis Changxing's faction.

838
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,880
I was just worrying about

839
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:54,750
not having enough people
to make an example of.

840
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:55,760
Go ahead and handle it.

841
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,620
Don't worry about anything else.

842
00:36:59,230 --> 00:36:59,670
Yes.

843
00:37:00,590 --> 00:37:01,140
Mentor.

844
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,280
In that case,

845
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,610
there's no time to lose.

846
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:04,280
I

847
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:05,620
will go back now

848
00:37:06,030 --> 00:37:07,430
to prepare for the trial.

849
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:08,760
Okay.

850
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:34,360
Mentor.

851
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:40,000
You always manage to come up with a plan

852
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:42,250
whenever it comes to Jiuheng.

853
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,150
Isn't it all

854
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:44,500
for you, Mentor?

855
00:37:45,030 --> 00:37:46,000
When I was in prison,

856
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,130
I wondered every day

857
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:49,660
who sent Ye Xian to go to Shanxi,

858
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,840
and how he managed
to get there so quickly.

859
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,300
Later I also recalled that

860
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:54,280
not long ago,

861
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:56,230
when Prince Ruichang rebelled,

862
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:58,150
Ye Xian entered the palace

863
00:37:58,150 --> 00:37:59,880
at precisely the right moment.

864
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:02,030
Putting these two things together,

865
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:02,800
I dare say

866
00:38:03,510 --> 00:38:04,880
someone among our people

867
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:06,280
has long been secretly

868
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:08,030
colluding with Ye Xian.

869
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:13,190
You think this person is...

870
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:14,720
This person can never be me,

871
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:16,150
let alone you.

872
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:17,690
As for He Wenxin,

873
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:20,480
he just wants to be a Grand Secretary
who avoids politics.

874
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:21,480
And has never had any ties

875
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:23,510
with the Marquis Changxing's household.

876
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:25,170
Then who else is left among us?

877
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:28,930
There is only Jiuheng.

878
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:31,800
Unless Jiuheng takes
heavy-handed measures this time

879
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:33,760
to severely punish Marquis Changxing,

880
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:34,560
otherwise...

881
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:41,880
Third Master.

882
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:45,280
[Thrice Reflections Against Greed;
Ninefold Virtues in the Sound of the Qin]

883
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,680
News came from Mr. Jiang.

884
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:44,810
As you expected,

885
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,630
Wang Xuanfan went to

886
00:38:46,630 --> 00:38:48,430
the Senior Grand Secretary's residence
early this morning

887
00:38:48,430 --> 00:38:49,890
and hasn't come out since.

888
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:51,480
He's been trying to sow doubt

889
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:52,940
about me in Mentor's mind.

890
00:38:58,590 --> 00:39:00,150
Go tell the Penal Court.

891
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:02,430
Early tomorrow morning,

892
00:39:03,070 --> 00:39:05,400
I'll interrogate Ye Xian and the Marquis.

893
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:11,220
I don't need you
to stay in prison with me!

894
00:39:13,960 --> 00:39:14,440
Father.

895
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:16,320
Your wounds haven't healed yet.

896
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,120
Stop talking.

897
00:39:21,870 --> 00:39:23,500
It seems this time Fu Hailian

898
00:39:24,230 --> 00:39:25,830
is determined to see me dead.

899
00:39:26,030 --> 00:39:27,550
And you still came in here with me.

900
00:39:27,550 --> 00:39:29,030
Do you think that makes you filial?

901
00:39:29,030 --> 00:39:29,940
How foolish!

902
00:39:30,590 --> 00:39:32,190
Find a way to get out of here quickly

903
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:33,140
and protect your mother

904
00:39:33,140 --> 00:39:34,220
and your sister.

905
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:37,520
If the marquisate is gone, then so be it.

906
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:41,030
You never wanted
to inherit the title anyway.

907
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:44,080
Stop talking.

908
00:39:45,510 --> 00:39:46,000
Please.

909
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:52,890
Why are you here?

910
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,030
Greetings,

911
00:40:03,090 --> 00:40:03,930
My Lord.

912
00:40:07,590 --> 00:40:08,880
Did Fu Hailian

913
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,490
send you to interrogate me?

914
00:40:11,110 --> 00:40:13,640
Why didn't he come
to interrogate me himself?

915
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:15,610
He hides behind others all day

916
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:17,150
and plays tricks.

917
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,740
And he still has the nerve to claim

918
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:22,070
it's for the country and the people.

919
00:40:24,870 --> 00:40:27,600
The Senior Grand Secretary
is occupied with many affairs

920
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:29,400
and may not be able to come in person.

921
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:29,960
But

922
00:40:30,360 --> 00:40:31,360
I will certainly

923
00:40:31,430 --> 00:40:32,360
relay your words

924
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:33,850
to him.

925
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:39,510
My son

926
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:41,850
is naturally a bit foolish.

927
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:44,700
He was afraid I'd suffer here,

928
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,930
so he came to keep me company in prison.

929
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:49,320
This matter has nothing to do with him.

930
00:40:50,190 --> 00:40:51,380
Let him go first.

931
00:40:51,590 --> 00:40:52,050
Father.

932
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:52,760
Shut up!

933
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:57,170
Your deep love for your son

934
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,810
really touches me, My Lord.

935
00:41:00,030 --> 00:41:00,550
But

936
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,090
I'm afraid you still don't know

937
00:41:03,110 --> 00:41:04,150
that Young Lord Ye

938
00:41:04,170 --> 00:41:05,440
almost stabbed me

939
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:06,830
to death on the street.

940
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:09,170
It's pure luck that I can still be here

941
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,840
questioning you today.

942
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,500
As for the food in this prison,

943
00:41:13,710 --> 00:41:15,310
I doubt you and Young Lord Ye

944
00:41:15,590 --> 00:41:16,810
would be able to eat it

945
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:17,810
or get used to it.

946
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:20,060
Then don't eat it.

947
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,250
Take it all away.

948
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,810
Chen Yanyun, how dare you!

949
00:41:24,030 --> 00:41:25,090
What are you doing?

950
00:41:26,230 --> 00:41:27,380
I

951
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:29,190
am the chief interrogator of this case.

952
00:41:29,190 --> 00:41:30,230
Young Lord Ye,

953
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:32,980
you'd better think carefully
before you speak.

954
00:41:36,190 --> 00:41:36,790
My Lord,

955
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:38,280
the prisoners are still awaiting trial.

956
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:40,540
We can't afford to have them die, My Lord.

957
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,550
Bring the Marquis out.

958
00:41:48,550 --> 00:41:48,920
Yes.

959
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:50,130
Guards.

960
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:11,510
Ask whatever you want.

961
00:42:11,510 --> 00:42:13,920
I have a clear conscience.

962
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:16,360
I have

963
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:17,880
nothing to ask.

964
00:42:20,560 --> 00:42:23,670
[Confession of Marquis Changxing]

965
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,550
These are my charges?

966
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,550
It's a confession.

967
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:34,050
You have admitted to your crimes

968
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:35,100
without dispute.

969
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,300
All that is left

970
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:37,890
is for you to sign it.

971
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:02,080
Third Master.

972
00:43:10,350 --> 00:43:12,610
When a nation is on the brink of collapse,

973
00:43:12,910 --> 00:43:15,840
treacherous officials like you
are bound to emerge.

974
00:43:16,710 --> 00:43:18,510
Even if it costs me my life,

975
00:43:19,330 --> 00:43:21,660
I will rid the country
of evil men like you.

976
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:25,820
What a Marquis Changxing.

977
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:27,900
Truly majestic.

978
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:29,510
But don't forget,

979
00:43:30,380 --> 00:43:32,230
your son is still in my hands.

980
00:43:44,980 --> 00:43:48,580
[A Splendid Match]
